headline: C.H. Robinson price target raised to $194 from $165 at TD Cowen
summary: TD Cowen raised the firm’s price target on C.H. Robinson (CHRW) to $194 from $165 and keeps a Hold rating on the shares. The firm noted they beat consensus expectations in Q4 and managed to post year-over-year adj.
